programme.title: Cinta Kau Dan Aku Ep12
programme.desc: Mengisahkan selepas kematian bapanya, Risya hidup dalam serba kekurangan dan sejak itu dia mengubah penampilannya menjadi seorang yang kasar. Risya tidak dapat meneruskan pelajaran ke universiti dan terpaksa membantu ibunya berniaga di warung. Kemudian dia mengambil keputusan untuk mengikut temannya, Milah berhijrah dan bekerja di Kuala Lumpur sebagai pemandu peribadi kepada majikan Milah iaitu tokoh korporat yang terkenal. Dengan kesungguhannya, Risya berjaya meyakinkan majikannya untuk diterima bekerja. Bagaimanapun tiada siapa menyedari dalam diam Farish Hakimi jatuh hati terhadap Risya dan kesempatan yang ada digunakan sepenuhnya lelaki itu apabila ibu Risya jatuh sakit, dia segera menghulurkan bantuan kos pembedahan penyakit jantungnya. Rasa terhutang budi dengan lelaki itu membuatkan ibu Risya menyarankan agar Farish Hakimi mengahwini anaknya Risya.

programme.desc: Rahman dan Zainab mempunyai 7 anak, dan seorang anak nya yang baru lahir bernama Adi. Rahman telah meletakkan Adi di sebuah masjid yang jauh dari daerah rumahnya kerana dia tidak lagi mampu untuk menjaga anaknya itu. Hussin pula seorang penagih dadah telah terdengar bayi menangis dan segera mendekati bayi tersebut kalau-kalau ada duit pada bayi itu, tetapi tiada langsung duit hanya ada surat beranak dan botol susu kecil. Mak Jah dan Pak Akob hairan kenapa ada bayi di rumah Hussin, lalu Hussin memberitahu bahawa anak itu adalah anak kakaknya yang baru sahaja meninggal dunia. Mak Jah telah menawarkan dirinya untuk menjaga Adi kalau-kalau Hussin sibuk. Samad, kawan kepada Hussin telah temukan pembeli bayi tersebut iaitu Helmi dan Zana. Dia ceritakan hal itu kepada Hajar. Sally bertemu Hajar dan beri amaran, sebaliknya Hajar membalas bahawa dia tahu tujuan Sally untuk membolot harta keluarga sehingga Maya dibuang keluarga dan kemudian membalas dendam dengan menolak Haikal. programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti Ep15
programme.desc: Haikal semakin pulih dan terkejut aunty Sally datang menjenguknya. Dia mahu Haikal rahsiakan bahawa dia yang tolak Haikal jatuh tangga. Hasrat Hisyam untuk membeli Warisan Art Gallery terkubur apabila ada pembeli lain membelinya dengan harga yang lebih tinggi. Sumayah@ Maya dapat merasakan kekecewaan suaminya. Dalam diam Maya bertemu Daniel, sepupu Zarif yang membeli galeri tersebut. Mereka adalah rakan kongsi perniagaan. Zarif masih di luar negra dan tidak dapat melupakan Maya. Maya terkejut dan begitu kecewa dengan perbuatan Zarif. Dia luahkan isi hatinya pada Daniel tentang pengorbanan Hisyam. Beberapa hari kemudian, Daniel mahu menjual semula galeri itu pada Hisyam dengan harga 1.9 juta. Hisyam tekad akan berusaha lebih demi mendapatkannya. Sally dan Arman sering bertengkar, Sally nekad untuk bercerai. Dia bertelagah dengan Hajar di pejabat Edruce Airlines. Keesokannya Arman nasihatkan Hajar mencari kerja lain atas saranan Tn Rahim. Arman beritahu Hajar dia akan ceraikan Sally setelah mendapat separuh saham syarikat. Zakiah terdengar rancangan dan kesalahan Arman dan Hajar memesongkan duit syarikat untuk tujuan peribadi. Zakiah memulakan siasatannya. Akibat terlalu tertekan dengan beberapa kejadian yang menimpa Sally, mengambil pil depression. Dia ditemui tersungkur di tepi katil oleh Pn Mahani, disyaki menelan pil berlebihan dos. Kebelakangan ini, Maya kerap mual dan sakit di sekitar rusuk kanan, dia ke klinik mendapatkan nasihat doktor. Doktor mahu jalankan ujian untuk mengenalpasti penyakit Maya.

programme.desc: Kisah kehidupan punkers berjumpa dengan musafir di bulan Ramadan. Oleh kerana adik beradik ramai dan rumah sempit, Pang banyak habiskan masa di tempat kerjanya, sebuah kedai cuci kereta Pokok Ketapang.

Kerusi Panas : dua orang tetamu mengambil bahagian dalam permainan "teka-teki" 2. playback sidekick memaparkan dua cerita pendek berjudul- dato dan datin menghadiri jamuan, dato dan janda. 3. 11 soalan : menampilkan Jiggy Masin menjawab 11 soalan umum mengenai dirinya. 4. dua orang tetamu menyertai permainan " Teka Nama Perkerjaan" 5. Dato' Ac Mizal mempersembahkan sebuah lagu.

programme.title: Perang Bibir Ep03
programme.desc: Dalam episod ketiga ini, 3 lagi peserta telah mengambil bahagian iaitu:- 1. Daler Yusuf 2. Zulin Aziz 3. Shireen Munir Mereka terlibat dalam persembahan Lip Sync Bertema, Mini Game # 1, Mini Game # 2 dan Lip Sync Spontan. Keputusan persembahan ini berpihak kepada Zulin yang mengumpul 180 markah dan layak ke pertandingan berikutnya.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep14
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani masih merajuk dan Mizan masih memujuknya. Di pejabat, Dzul berbincang dengan Mizan tentang Shariff. Nizam yang berjumpa Hani tempuh hari juga berhasrat Hani terima tawaran temuduga kerja di Johor, lagi pun dia juga dapat kerja baru di Johor. Hani hanya menjawab soal itu dia perlu berbincang dengan Mizan. Dengan situasi begitu, Nizam bertekad akan perolehi juga Hani dan sekali lagi dia meminta Suraya melakukan porak peranda di rumah tangga Hani/Mizan. Sementara itu, Sheila juga bertekad agar Nizam tetap akan dicari dan didampinginya. Di pejabat, Mizan berkongsi dan menceritakan situasi dia dengan isterinya kepada Dzul antara yang terpenting Mizan memang mengharapkan satu ketika dia akan menceraikan isterinya secara baik. Selain itu, mengakui tidak pernah menyentuh isterinya pun. Mizan juga diarah untuk menguruskan satu projek syarikat di luar negara. Semasa Hani hadir temuduga, dia juga tidak menyangka orang yang akan menemuduga itu Shariff. Kebetulan Mizan datang berjumpa Shariff hendak bercakap hal pekerjaan, semasa dia memasuki ke bilik Shariff, Hani bersembunyi ditepi meja

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir Ep13
programme.desc: Sekembalinya ke Malaysia, Zafuan maklumkan Juliana dahpun jadi tunang Aidid. Tapi Aidid rahsiakan dari Suzan. Dia bawa Suzan jumpa Haryati untuk terus-terang yang mereka dah bernikah. Tapi Suzan dikejutkan kenyataan pertunangan Aidid dan Juliana. Haryati juga takkan maafkan dia gara-gara babanya. Haryati ugut Aidid nikah juga dengan Juliana, jika tak Aidid akan disingkirkan dari jawatan CEO. Malah Haryati dan Juliana turut jumpa Suzan dan hina dia sebagai perampas dan ambil kesempatan atas kedudukan Aidid. Akhirnya Aidid tak tahan lalu ambil keputusan letak jawatan.

programme.title: Perang Bibir Ep02
programme.desc: Perang Bibir merupakan satu realiti TV, di mana 24 peserta akan mengambil bahagian. 3 peserta di episod ini yang akan mengambil bahagian, iaitu Izzue Islam, Taufiq Hanafi dan Mawar Rashid. Mereka perlu beraksi dengan menggerakkan bibir mereka tanpa suara (lip sync) seperti mereka sedang menyanyi mengikut lirik lagu yang dipilih oleh mereka. Kali ini juga, dua mini game perlu dilakukan mereka iaitu meneka bibir penyanyi dan tiupan tisu. Di akhir perang bibir kali ini, Mawar Rashid muncul juara mengumpul 203 markah mengalah Izzue Islam yang mengumpul 160 markah dan Taufiq Hanafi 122 markah. Mawar Rashid akan mara ke pusingan seterusnya. Manakala, yang kalah akan disenaraikan dalam "wild card" sehingga 24 peserta selesai

programme.desc: Hos Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero membawa penonton ke Nafas Cube @ Mardi, Serdang. Mereka terus memperkenalkan kemudahan sedia ada di tempat penginapan tersebut. Selain daripada mengunjungi G2G Animal Garden untuk mengenali secara lebih rapat pelbagai jenis haiwan, mereka juga melawat House of Kambing untuk menikmati sup kambing yang enak. Aktiviti-aktiviti lain yang dilakukan termasuk melawat Ladang Mini Kelulut untuk merasai manisan madu asli dan menunggang kuda di Majlis Ekuine Malaysia. programme.desc: Semenjak Nuzul berhenti kerja dan menjadi suri rumah sepenuh masa, kehidupannya terasa bosan. Menjadi suri rumah menjarakkan lagi hubungannya dengan Irsyad. Nuzul buntu. Kadang-kala Nuzul akan ke Rayyan Café untuk bertemu Laila. Laila dan Saiful ada juga cuba mengorek dengannya tentang punca dia melarikan diri dulu namun Nuzul tetap tetap dengan pendiriannya. Dia tidak akan membocorkan rahsianya itu kerana dia takut hal itu akan menggoyahkan hubungan ibu dan anak.

programme.desc: Bola, matahari, pinggan makan. Adakah anda tahu apakah persamaan antara semua item ini?

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti Ep16
programme.desc: Sumayah@ Maya kdisahkan mengidap Sirosis iaitu kegagalan fungsi hati. Menurut Dr Rohaya, dia perlu segera mendapatkan transplan hati. Maya banyak termenung dan menangis sendirian selepas mengetahui penyakitnya tetapi dia cuba sembunyikan di hadapan Hisyam. Hisyam dapat lihat perubahan sikap isterinya dan semakin lesu. Dia minta Maya berehat dan tak perlu lagi siapkan tempahan. Mahani tahu suaminya sering teringatkan Syifa dan Haikal yang sudah lama tidak datang ke rumah kerana dihalang Maya, akibat kejadian tempoh hari yang terjadi pada Haikal. Mahani pujuk agar Rahim memafkan anak menantunya. Atas kerjasama Saiful mendapatkan bahan bukti kes penyelewengan duit syarikat, akhirnya Hajar dan Arman ditahan pihak polis. Sementara itu, Zakiah dan Saiful bakal mengikat tali pertunangan. Hisyam berjaya mendapatkan semula hak ke atas Warisan Art Gallery. Dia terkejut apabila Daniel memberitahu Maya bertemunya. Sally pula sering bersendirian dibayangi rasa bersalahnya terhadap Maya dulu. Ia adalah karma kerana sikap tamaknya mahu membolot Edruce Airlines. Dia menceritakan segala kebenaran kepada ibunya. Suatu hari, Maya terserempak dengan Zakiah bersama Dr Rohaya ketika hendak membeli barang dan mereka saling mengenali. Ketika Zakiah beredar, Dr Rohaya bertanyakan sebab Maya tidak hadir temujanji dan minta Maya segera dapatkan rawatan lanjut untuk pembedahan pemindahan hati

programme.title: Bila Bujang Masuk Dapur S3 Ep04
programme.desc: Memaparkan dua selebriti yang tidak pulang ke kampung memasak beberapa hidangan untuk menyambut kehadiran sahabat handai. Tetamu jemputan, artis komedi Faiz Tapaw. Mereka telah menyediakan hidangan Serunding Ikan Bilis, Ketupat Palas, Emping Jagung Tomyam dan Air Nenas Soda Bujang Style. Mereka meraikan tetamu Falisha Crossley untuk bersama-sama menikmati jamuan itu.

programme.title: Surprise Surprise Four
programme.desc: R adalah untuk Race

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S9 Ep04
programme.desc: Andi mengetahui semua kebohongan ini karena mendengar pembicaraan Haris dengan Riri. Andi sangat kecewa dengan memilih pergi dan menceraikan Riri. Riri terkejut saat menerima surat dari pengadilan agama dan menelpon Haris. Semuanya pun takut Andi sudah mengetahui tentang kehamilan Riri. Di saat itu Karin datang dengan membawa bukti dan menjelaskan kalau semua ini ulah Tanti. Tanti tidak bisa mengelak lagi dan berhasil kabur. Tanti masih berniat mencelakakan Riri lagi karena cemburu melihat Riri-Haris berduaan.

programme.title: Kaki Bahan S4 Ep06
programme.desc: Andi yang mengetahui kebohongan Haris dan Riri menculik Doni yang sedang sakit. Namun Andi tidak tega melihat Doni yang makin parah dan akhirnya membawanya ke rumah sakit. Saat dia ada di rumah sakit Iren mengetahui keberadaan Andi. RIRI menciumi Doni sambil menangis tersedu-sedu. SINTA memeriksa keadaan DONI. Dia tertegun. Semua orang pun mengetahui jika Tanti adalah orang yang jahat. Sementara itu Andi menggeliat kesakitan dan akhirnya Andi meninggal. Haris dan Riri pun akhirnya menikah.

programme.title: Homegrown Show S6 Ep03
programme.desc: Homegrown Show kini kembali, memaparkan persembahan muzik berlainan genre dari artis serta kugiran tanah air pada masa kini. Episod ini adalah focus kepada Raja Syahiran & Bheart dengan genre hiphop & R&B.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep15
programme.desc: Memaparkan ketika Hani masih bersembunyi di bilik pejabat Shariff, Mizan datang berkaitan kerja dan kesempatan itu Mizan telah menceritakan segalanya bagaimana dia berkahwin dengan Hani. Antara yang terpenting, Mizan akui dia masih tiada perasaan terhadap Hani dan semata-mata membahagia perasaan ibu bapanya. Hani kemudiannya terus pulang dan bersedih. Sesekali Hani mengimbas semasa dia dan Nizam di alam persekolahan, ketika itu pun Nizam telah menyuara untuk berkahwin. Walau pun begitu, Hani selepas bersembahyang memohon doa agar hati suaminya berubah dan tetap padanya. Shariff pula bertekad dan berbincang dengan Dzul yakni secara baik berharap Hani diceraikan Mizan dan dia akan menjadikan Hani isterinya. Suraya masih dengan dunia kehidupannya, sering bertukar lelaki, disamping menjadi perempuan simpanan Fuad. Hidup berfoyanya pernah ternampak oleh Mizan. Nizam terus mengugut Suraya berperanan supaya berlaku penceraian antara Hani dan Mizan. Nizam juga terus bertekad menjadikan Hani isterinya. Sheila pula tetap mencari Nizam yang kini di Johor Bahru untuk bersamanya.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir Ep14
programme.desc: Aidid bawa Suzan balik rumah keluarga Sy Kamarudin untuk mula hidup baru. Aidid nak buka café konsep taman. Tok Ayah dan Tok Umi seronok terima mereka. Tapi tidak Sh Kamariah. Dia masih dingin walaupun Aidid cuba bantu dia cari bisnes baru. Sh Kamariah buat hal nak sakitkan hati Suzan. Tapi akhirnya dia sedar yang Suzan ikhlas dengan keluarganya. Haryati pula hadapi masalah bila kebanyakan pelanggan hanya mahu berurusan dengan Aidid. Apalagi bila Zafuan juga hantar notis berhenti kerja. Akhirnya Haryati hubungi Aidid minta dia balik KL. Aidid kembali dilema.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Episod ke 3 antara lain memaparkan Nia seolah-olah bertemu dengan tuan puteri tetapi sangkaan meleset bila dia memaklumkan kepada Shasa kerana dia membayang patung di ruang tengah rumah sebagai tuan puteri. Sementara itu perangai pelik Fauzan yang sering menyatakan di sisinya ada Roserita terus menjadijadi lalu menghairan dan merisaukan Datin Salina. Manakala di suatu malam lembaga putih telah mengganggui Pak Abas membuatkan Roslan memanggil Ibrahim untuk mengubatinya. Nia pula terus terasa ada makhluk menggangguinya, kali ini di bilik air dimana dia ternampak satu wayah dicermin, sesekali dia terlihat tuan puteri cantik muncul sekejap di rumahnya. Agak menakutkan lembaga hitam pun juga menggangguinya juga. Kemuncaknya ketika dia sedang tidur tuan puteri menghampirinya dan ingin memberi sekuntum bunga cempaka, tiba-tiba Nia terjaga.

programme.title: Juara
programme.desc: Bisma, seorang remaja yang mempunyai bakat seni mempertahankan diri semula jadi menyukai Bella, seorang gadis di kolejnya. Tetapi teman lelakinya, Attar sentiasa mengganggu Bisma sehingga seorang lelaki misteri melatihnya untuk melawan.

programme.title: Plan B Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Que dan Mica, pada mulanya tidak bersetuju Khai menerima cadangan daripada seorang pelajar kolej, Airis untuk mencuri kereta, namun setelah Khai memberi alasannya, mereka bukan mahu terlibat secara serius dalam aktiviti itu, tetapi semata-mata sebagai hiburan sahaja, kemudian Que dan Mica bersetuju. Sementara King yang terlibat dalam penyeludupan kereta mewah ke sempadan Thailand, sedang merancang sesuatu bersama-sama pembantunya untuk mengubah strategi mereka supaya tidak terperangkap dalam sekatan polis.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Episod Pertama cereka komedi seram disusuli dengan kepercayaan khurafat ini berkisar kepada personaliti Nia. Nia sebagai setiausaha syarikat milik seorang Datin Salina yang amat menyukainya hingga bercadang untuk dijodohkan kepada anak lelakinya. Ibu Nia dikampung, sedang sakit dijagai oleh Roslan, bapa saudaranya (Pak Lang). Nia mempercayai dia wajar menyeru puteri yang sesekali Nia akan lakukan bertujuan melindunginya dan juga sebagai amalan turun temurunnya selama ini. Jika tidak dilakukan, saka berbentuk syaitan akan menggangguinya. Ada sebab-sebab bahawa ibunya memiliki saka dan kematiannya bererti saka itu cuba mempengaruhi warisnya iaitu Nia. Nia tinggal dengan Shasa dan sepupu Shasa iaitu, Adrus adalah 'boy friend' Nia. Adrus sedang menceburi kerjaya dalam bidang paranormal, merupakan anak Ibrahim seorang bomoh. Ketika ibu Nia meninggal dunia dia belum ketahui. Sementara itu, semasa pengembumian ibunya berlaku juga kekecuhan iaitu muncul lembaga putih (berbentuk manusia - wanita). Selain dari itu, sesekali saka Gelam berbentuk syaitan (hitam jalur hijau) mengganggui Nia, 'boy friend'nya dan pernah bersama lembaga putih mengganggui bomoh Ibrahim.

programme.desc: Awang yang menguasai Long Hussin kini terus menghitung mangsa.masih ada beberapa mangsa lagi yang perlu dihabiskan nyawa mereka. Shasa hanya menyatakan kerana Nia terbawa-bawa dan memikirkan yang dia alami. Sementara itu, Pak Abas dan Roslan bercakap tentang arwah Rosserita. Di pejabat, Nia diganggui oleh saka Gelam. Manakala di rumah dia terserempak depan berdepan dengan lembaga putih berdialog dan memberi amaran kepadanya. Kemudiannnya menceritakan pengalamannya bahawa lembaga putih itu menyerupai emaknya. Manakala Fauzan dengan ibunya bertengkar kerana ibunya bercadang untuk menghantar ke hospital gila. Ini berikutan Fauzan bercakap dengan seseorang kononnya berada di atas bangku disebelahnya.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai menjalani latihan teknik mencuri kereta-kereta mewah daripada EncikBoon dan disaksikan oleh Airis dan Mica. Sementara itu, Que ketika dalam tahanan, telah memberi informasi kepada polis mengenai kegiatan lumba kereta haram oleh ketua kumpulan, Jim. Que telah dibebaskan, setelah dijamin oleh ibunya dan dia berjanji untuk tidak terlibat dalam aktiviti haram yang dilakukan oleh kawan-kawannya. Dalam satu serbuan pihak polis telah berjaya memberkas salah seorang daripada kumpulan lumba haram itu.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan encik Bad kini sedar kekasinya telah menipunya, kononnya wang RM 5,000 yang diberi pinjam untuk kos rawatan, sebaliknya kekasihnya telah menghilangkan diri. Anak dan isteri yang dicerainya telah menyindir-nyindirnya. Sementara itu Adam, Shah dan Daniel terus berusaha mencari lembaga lilin yang diharapkan encik Bad. Sementara itu Nur juga berselfie dengan Shah dan di tengah gambar mereka wujud lembaga lilin, menjadi kerisauan Nur. Nur mengadu kepada ibunya dan di samping itu Nur juga bertindak menjadi perantaraan agar ibu dan bapanya berbaik semula. Shah, Adam dan Daniel telah berbincang dengan profesor dan mendapat nasihat lanjut tentang sukarnya lembaga lilin untuk ditangkap. Di samping itu, Shah dan Adam masih berusaha memikat Nur walaupun Nur membayangkan dia menyukai Shah. Adam juga mengesyaki Shah memikat Nur tetapi masih berpura-pura. Usaha yang berterusan dengan bantuan rakan wanita Daniel, akhirnya lembaga lilin muncul dan dengan mensasarkan lilin hingga padam, akhirnya lembaga lilin berjaya ditangkap dan mengembirakan encik Bad kerana muzuimnya di kunjungi ramai

programme.title: Ong Bak 3
programme.desc: Kisah pahlawan Tien, yang telah ditangkap oleh panglima perang yang kejam Tuan Rajasena. Tien melarikan diri daripada cengkaman Rajasena, pulih daripada kecederaannya yang melumpuhkan dengan bantuan Guru Bua, dan kembali untuk berhadapan dengan Bhuti Sangkha, yang telah menggantikan Rajasena sebagai penjahat utama.

programme.title: Bodyguard S1 Ep9
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nasha perlukan maklumat lanjut dari Ryan siapa dirinya sebenar. Ryan sebagai bodyguard kepada Dato' Amir berjaya memujuk Mak Jah berjumpa dengan Dato' Amir selepas didesak. Mak Jah memberitahu Dato' Amir bahawa Nasha sebenarnya anak mereka. Nasha akhirnya di bawa berjumpa kedua ibu bapanya. Dalam kes berasingan, Farish bodyguard Adam berjaya melepaskan Adam dari cengkaman Kumpulan Kobra. Adam akhirnya menyerahkan buku daftar senarai nama ahli Kumpulan Kobra kepada Farish. Danial, bodyguard kepada Eliza dimaklumkan bahawa Makcik Azizah adalah bekas isteri Dato' Zaidi. Ini bermakna Rashid adalah abang Eliza, mereka tidak boleh berkahwin. Eliza merajuk dan mahu meninggalkan keluarganya. Rahul pula sebagai bodyguard Maya telah dimarahi Maya kerana selalu menyebelahi Boboy. Maya masih tidak membenarkan Boboy berjumpa dengan Mikhail bekas suami Maya. Semua maklumat ini dilaporkan kepada ketuanya Nasha secara harian. Di akhir episod, ibu bapa Farish bersetuju menerima Nasha sebagai menantu mereka

Sementara itu dia juga menceritakan bahawa Puteri Jarum Permata adalah menjadi amalan keluarganya sebagai pelindung, tetapi akhirnya ini saka Gelam suka mengganguinya bila dia hendak datang. Dalam pada itu dengan tiba-tiba, Pak Abas dirasuk oleh saka Gelam, tetapi dapat dipulihkan oleh Ibrahim. Manakala Ibrahim setelah bekerjasama dengan kumpulan aktivis paranormal telah dapat berkomunikasi dengan lembaga putih. Kesempatan itu dia telah memberi amaran agar jangan ganggu sesiapa. Manakala saka Gelam telah berkomunikasi dengan lembaga putih lalu memberi amaran dan marahmarah. Dalam pada itu Ibrahim yang terpikat dengan Zeti telah membuat satu janji temu. Di pertemuan itu, Zeti yang bermata duitan juga berkecimpung belajar memuja-memuja orang agar terpengaruh. Dia tahu Datin Salina banyak wang dan bermasalah kerana anak lelakinya tidak setuju dijodohkan dengan Nia. Dengan itu Zeti telah mengajak Ibrahim mencari jalan agar Nia sukakan anak Datin Salina. Dalam situasi ini Ibrahim menolak membuatkan Zeti merajuk dan beredar.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep6
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah bagaimana Imran yang masih sesat di hutan bertemu seekor jin bernama Rakib yang membantunya keluar. Semenjak peristiwa itu Imran sering di datangi Rakib yang cuba memberi peringatan tentang sesuatu perkara buruk akan berlaku namun tidak diendah Imran. Prilaku Imran yang seolah-olah bercakap bersendirian ketika berbicara dengan Rakib sempat dilihat oleh Maira yang yakin bahawa kuasa magik Imran ada kaitan dengan kuasa jin.Maira cuba berkongsi apa yang telah dilihat tentang Imran besama Zara yang kebetulan datang untuk menunjuk kuasa magik yang dia miliki. Maira yang keliru serta takut apabila mendapat tahu Imran, Haikal dan Zara memiliki kuasa magik enggan mendekati dan berkawan dengan mereka lagi.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep1112

programme.title: Ghost Writer 2
programme.desc: Naya, seorang novelis dan bekerja sebagai penulis skrip di sebuah syarikat. Di tengah-tengah cubaan untuk bertahan dengan kakaknya, Darto, Naya sekali lagi terpaksa berhadapan dengan hantu.

programme.title: Baginda

Hampir sahaja putus asa namun sikap dedikasinya untuk mendidik anak bangsa membuatkan Azian ingin terus menjalankan amanah pakciknya.

programme.title: Bukan Cinta Malaikat
programme.desc: Reyhan, seorang sukarelawan Muslim Care yang berasal dari Bandung jatuh hati kepada gadis Malaysia bernama Dewi sejak dia menyelamatkan Dewi daripada satu insiden ketika mereka berada di Madinah. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta Reyhan itu terhalang apabila Dewi mempunyai kekasih bernama Adam. Dalam masa yang sama, seorang gadis bernama Aliyah pula menaruh hati kepada Reyhan.

programme.title: Gila - Gila Pengantin Remaja
programme.desc: Pasangan remaja yang bakal menduduki peperiksaan SPM, Amir dan Mastura berikrar ingin berkahwin selepas tamatnya pengajian di universiti. Namun, Fandi yang juga rakan sekelas Mastura mencemburui percintaan mereka. SPM pun tiba tetapi Mastura terlewat menghadiri ujian Matematik dan berasa amat kecewa kerana menganggap dia telah pun gagal. Kakak Mastura, Anita pula ingin Mastura mencari calon suami yang kaya. Perasaan kecewa mula menyelubungi diri Amir apabila mendapat tahu Mastura ditunangkan dengan Fandi. Mengetahui perihal sebenar mengapa mereka akan dikahwinkan, Amir membawa Mastura lari ke selatan Thailand. Bermulalah kekecohan antara mereka semua dalam sekuel kepada Gila-Gila Pengantin ini.

programme.title: XX Ray 2
programme.desc: Bekerja sebagai saintis kadet, Tina berasa ditipu apabila Johan mendakwa dia yang mencipta mesin pelupusan laser walhal ia merupakan hasil cetusan idea dari Tina. Ingin menghalang niat jahat Johan, Tina meminta bantuan Amir. Namun, keduanya terkena pancaran laser mesin itu dalam cubaan untuk menghalang Johan dan telah dihantar ke zaman Kesultanan Melayu Melaka.

programme.title: Puteri Impian 2
programme.desc: Gadis kilang yang menolak lamaran seorang kerabat diraja Tengku Faizal, menaruh hati terhadap jurukamera stesen televisyen, Zul. Nora menyukai Zul tetapi dia telah pun menjalin hubungan bersama Lisa. Adik kepada Tengku Faizal, Tengku Farid ingin membawa semula Nora kembali ke abangnya. Tekad, dia ingin mengangkat semula maruah abangnya.

programme.title: Baginda
programme.desc: Diwariskan untuk mengurus sebuah kolej swasta di Johor Bahru oleh pakciknya, Azian terpaksa melalui pelbagai cabaran untuk menaikkan semula martabat sekolah yang sudah merudum prestasinya itu. Hampir sahaja putus asa namun sikap dedikasinya untuk mendidik anak bangsa membuatkan Azian ingin terus menjalankan amanah pakciknya.

programme.title: Jengka
programme.desc: Nini mengalami keguguran semasa melarikan diri di ladang kelapa sawit. Namun, satu perkara aneh terjadi apabila bayinya dikatakan masih hidup dan dilarikan oleh penunggu. Orang kampung berusaha membantu mencari Nini dan anaknya, namun perkara seram terjadi sepanjang pencarian mereka.

programme.title: Gila - Gila Pengantin
programme.desc: Aliah seorang gadis yang ingin berkahwin tetapi mempunyai satu fobia dimana dia takut untuk bersanding dia atas pelamin setelah apa yang terjadi keatas dirinya semasa dia kecil. Dalam masa yang sama, Johari juga mempunyai masalah yang sama dengan Aliah. Mereka telah bertemu di dalam dunia cyber dan beramah mesra dengan perbualan masing-masing sehingga hari ini. Rupa-rupanya ada kenangan di antara mereka berdua. Namun mereka bakal berkahwin dengan pasangan yang berlainan dari mereka dan kedua-duanya perlu bersanding di atas pelamin ketika majlis perkahwinan.

programme.title: Femina
programme.desc: Perjuangan untuk mendapatkan hak setara antara jantina terutamanya wanita lantang dibicarakan di dalam majalah Femina. Tina, tegas memperjuangkan pendiriannya manakala Anita tidak berapa menyukai cara Tina. Femina telah menjadi satu platform anti-lelaki. Pertemuan Tina bersama Pyan mula mengubah pandangan ekstrem Tina namun perasaan dilema mula menguasai diri apabila dituduh sebagai pembelot wanita.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: Scoop
programme.desc: Tania, seorang wartawan menjalankan penyiasatan tentang kes pembunuhan rakannya, Johari yang menyiasat skandal syarikat kewangan. Skandal tersebut melibatkan bapa Sheila. Dibantu oleh seorang jurufoto, Norman yang ingin membersihkan namanya kerana sebelum Johari mati dibunuh, terdapat pertengkaran antara mereka berdua. Mereka pun mula menyiasat punca sebenar pembunuhan Johari.

programme.title: Puteri Impian
programme.desc: Pekerja kilang, Puteri Nora sentiasa mengimpikan untuk menjadi seorang puteri raja. Impiannya menjadi kenyataan apabila dia diterima menyertai pertandingan "Memburu Impian". Kehidupannya berubah sekelip mata apabila bertemu Tengku Faizal, seorang putera raja. Namun, Zul, jurukameranya dalam rancangan itu turut menyukai Puteri Nora. Pilihan harus dibuat antara kemewahan atau kebebasan.

programme.title: Azura 2012
programme.desc: Azura, seorang gadis remaja yang gigih hadapi cabaran hidup untuk mencapai cita-citanya. Dia tinggal bersama ibu saudaranya setelah kedua ibu bapanya meninggal dunia dalam satu tragedi. Azura kemudiannya menjadi mahasiswa di sebuah universiti swasta dan menjalinkan hubungan mesra dengan Zek, seorang anak hartawan. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta mereka dihalang oleh bapa Zek dan mereka terpaksa melalui pelbagai dugaan.

programme.title: Tersuka Dia
programme.desc: seorang gadis jatuh hati kepada seorang pemuda tampan yang merupakan ketua pegawai eksekutif di syarikat miliknya . Gadis itu mula tertarik kepada pemuda ini setelah beliau bantu mengejar peragut beg tangannya . Pemuda itu turut jatuh hati terhadap si gadis yang pernah membulinya semasa di sekolah dahulu

programme.title: Kl Zombie
programme.desc: Rutin harian Nipis berubah selepas malaysia dilanda wabak zombie. Ini bermula apabila salah seorang rakan nipis telah di gigit oleh anjing yang ada virus bahaya.

programme.title: Bukan Orang Buta
programme.desc: eorang pemuzik jalanan (busker) yang berbakat tetapi tidak diberi perhatian orang ramai telah menukar strateginya untuk menyamar sebagai seorang busker buta. Penyamarannya mula menarik perhatian ramai dan berjaya dilamar oleh sebuah syarikat muzik terkemuka.

programme.title: Jom Wayang S14 Ep16
programme.desc: Anda kaki wayang? Hos Elyssa Alia membawakan anda informasi menarik bagi filem-filem terpilih tempatan dan luar negara dengan cara yang berbeza yang pastinya akan membuat anda ketawa dan santai sambil menonton Jom Wayang

programme.title: Mv Seleksi Sinema Ep2
programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.title: Teacher Chan Ram
programme.desc: Chan Ram dibesarkan di sebuah kampung di mana ibu bapa sudah biasa menghantar anak perempuan mereka bekerja di Bangkok. Dia hanya tamat darjah 4 sahaja kerana tidak mampu untuk menyambung pelajaran. Bagaimanapun, dia membuka sekolah kecil untuk mengajar orang-orang bukit dengan sokongan ibu bapanya dan Siwapong rakan sekolahnya yang pulang ke kampung dan membantunya.

programme.title: Hujan Bulan Juni
programme.desc: Pingkan (Velove Vexia), seorang pensyarah muda di Universitas Sastera Jepang Indonesia, berpeluang belajar di Jepun selama dua tahun. Sarwono (Adipati Dolken) sedih mendengar berita bahawa dia akan ditinggalkan oleh Pingkan.

programme.title: Jeritan Batinku
programme.desc: Fauziah, anak yatim piatu didera oleh ibu saudaranya Ramlah. Fauziah meninggalkan rumah dan lari ke bandar. Sharif seorang ahli perniagaan telah membawa Fauziah ke rumahnya dan dijadikan sebagai anak angkatnya. Tetapi kehadirannya tidak disenangi oleh anak perempuan Sharif, Mahani. Sementara itu di kampung pula, Ramlah mengalami tekanan jiwa dan menjadi gila kerana merasa bersalah terhadap Fauziah selama ini.

programme.title: Tmo Kaki Kitai
programme.desc: Saksikan di sebalik tabir pembikinan Filem Kaki Kitai

programme.title: E-San Holy Trip
programme.desc: Sekumpulan rakan yang tidak berjumpa selama 10 tahun bertemu semula di pengebumian seorang rakan yang meninggal dunia akibat kemurungan. mendiang telah meninggalkan misteri untuk mereka pergi mengembara mencari sesuatu.

programme.title: Mv Seleksi Sinema Ep11
programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.title: Fainow
programme.desc: kisah pergolakan rumah tangga sepasang suami isteri selepas sang isteri mendapat tahu kecurangan suaminya.

programme.title: Jeman
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Jeman yang berusia 20an mengalami masalah lembam, ibunya meninggal dunia ketika melahirkannya.Jeman dibesarkan oleh neneknya Mak Wan. Manakala ayahnya Jalil sudah berkahwin lain.

programme.title: Andai Kita Berjodoh
programme.desc: Perlakuan biadap tunang Melda iaitu Marcel membuatkan dia berasa tertekan yang teramat. Marcel sentiasa memerhatikan Melda, dan itu membuatkan dia jengkel. Melda mendapat ketenangan di sisi Evan dalam keadaan itu.

programme.title: Cinta 2 Pilihan Ep109
programme.desc: Fathir dan Sukma merupakan pasangan suami isteri yang hidup bahagia dalam kesederhanaan di Magelang. Mereka mempunyai seorang anak perempuan bernama Zahra. Fathir bekerja sebagai kontraktor, dan Sukma hanya seorang suri rumah. Pada suatu hari, Fathir menerima projek besar. Malangnya, terdapat masalah dengan projek itu. Masalah timbul apabila Zahra disahkan menghidap penyakit kronik. Doktor mencadangkan agar Zahra menjalani rawatan di Jakarta.

programme.title: D'Koplo Ep11
programme.desc: D'Koplo (Musim 1) merupakan persembahan bakat nyanyian koplo dangdut pertama dari D'Koplo 2023. Juri utama musim ini terdiri daripada Soimah, Nassar, Dewi Perssik, dan Nita Thalia. Ada juga beberapa juri jempotan yang akan hadir.

programme.title: Golden Memories Asia Ep16
programme.desc: Golden Memories Asia merupakan acara pencarian bakat untuk menyanyikan lagu-lagu nostalgia atau lagu lama dari tahun 1970-an hingga 2000-an, dihadiri oleh enam negara Asia Tenggara iaitu Brunei Darussalam, Indonesia, Malaysia, Filipina, Singapura, dan Timor Leste. Program ini adalah untuk memupuk kegembiraan dan keseronokan, serta satu bentuk persahabatan antara negara.

programme.title: Waiting For Rain
programme.desc: An unmotivated student regains his passion for life after exchanging letters with his childhood friend and promise to meet if it rains on December 31st each year.

programme.title: I
programme.desc: Ah-Young who grew up in an orphanage becomes the babysitter of Young-Chae, who is raising a 6-month-old child on her own. One day, her child has an accident and she places all the blame on Ah-Young...

programme.title: Finding Mr. Destiny
programme.desc: Ji-woo is still hung up on a man she fell in love in her early twenties. Her worried father has no choice but to drag her to Gi-joon, who helps people to locate their long-lost first loves.

programme.title: One Day
programme.desc: A newly widowed insurance examiner takes a case involving a woman who is in a coma. When visits her at the hospital, he encounters her spirit and realizes he is the only person who can see her.

programme.title: The Battleship Island
programme.desc: During the colonial rule of Japan, around 400 Koreans are conscripted into slave labor on Hashima Island. As the island’s dark secrets are revealed, the Korean labourers plot to escape.

programme.title: Tunnel
programme.desc: While driving home for his daughter's birthday, a man gets trapped in a collapsed tunnel and struggles to survive with just two bottles of water, a birthday cake and a cell phone.

programme.title: Project Wolf Hunting
programme.desc: During the extradition to Korea, a group of dangerous criminals united to stage an escape from the floating prison.

programme.title: Innocent Witness
programme.desc: A housekeeper is charged with murder. Her attorney is surprised to learn the only witness to the crime is a teenage girl with Asperger's. Will the girl be able to provide a valid statement?

programme.title: The Con Artists
programme.desc: A wily safecracker is forced to help a mob boss pull off a $150 million heist, but smells a double-cross in the works.

programme.title: The Pension
programme.desc: When four different couples head to a motel for different reasons, truths are revealed and secrets are uncovered.

programme.title: C'Est Si Bon
programme.desc: The story of three young musicians formed a band after a music bar named ‘C’est Si Bon’, where they bicker over their music and find their muse.

programme.title: Remember You
programme.desc: A lawyer suffering from severe memory loss and a total change of character investigates his past and his connection to a woman he meets in a hospital.

programme.title: Gonjiam: Haunted Asylum
programme.desc: A handful of people are recruited to live stream a horror show at Gonjiam, Korea's most haunted hospital. To attract more viewers, scares are set up along the way, but soon things take a darker turn.

programme.title: Penny Pinchers
programme.desc: A money-saving young woman teams up with an unemployed loser in money-raising schemes, resulting in some hilarious mishaps and a blossoming romance.

programme.title: My Little Bride
programme.desc: A high school girl was forced to marry a college student by her grandfather. The effort to keep the marriage secret was soon challenged as her husband will be teaching in her school as an intern…

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep10731074
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.desc: "iWalker - West Eyes to the East" followed the host, Rifat who is a foreigner that traveled abroad, leading the audience to experience Taiwan, which has never been seen before.

programme.title: Stylish Man-The Chef (M) Ep3604
programme.desc: <Stylish Man – The Chef> is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng, Bernice Tsai and Genie Chuo, together with two professional chefs, A-Chi and James. There are two main themes for the program, which are “Big Stars Come to Cook” and “Five-Star Cooking Show”. <Stylish Man – The Chef> containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep10771078
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: Hot Door Night (M) Ep2036
programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa(T) Ep154
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: Dragon Master: Dragon Spell
programme.desc: The Dragon King is locked in a seal by the Dragon Master for 500 years, and his daughter must travel back in time to 500 years ago to kill the Dragon Master, in order to reverse the act. Little did she know that the Dragon King and Dragon Master were close friends back then…

programme.title: Running On Karma
programme.desc: Andy Lau is a monk turned body-builder, with the gift of foreseeing people's lives. He befriends a female cop (Cecilia Cheung) and uses his gift to change the force of Karma and her destiny. The movie is ultimately a Buddhist parable about the nature of karma.

programme.title: Fagara
programme.desc: After her father’s death, a Hong Kong girl discovers she has two hitherto unknown sisters, Branch and Cherry. Through taking up her late father’s hotpot restaurant, she reunites with her sisters by different mothers, and understands her father more from a different perspective, allowing her to finally resolve her long-time hard feelings with him.

programme.title: Undiscovered Tomb
programme.desc: On the remote border between China and India, adventurer Ivy scours the land in search of the undiscovered tomb rumored to house the long-lost Pills of Eternity. However, she is not the only one searching for these powerful pills.

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: My Country, My Parents
programme.desc: Set in 4 different eras in China, the 4-part anthology about ‘home and country’ is directed by Wu Jing, Zhang Zi Yi, Xu Zheng and Shen Teng, who also star in their own story. The movie depicts how the ‘fathers’ forge ahead through the struggle of times, defending strong family ties and passing on the ‘fighting’ spirit through generations.

programme.title: Cross
programme.desc: Lee believes people who commit suicide will go to hell. After his wife killed herself because of cancer, Lee feels the pain of people with suicidal thoughts and thinks of killing them to bring them to heaven. He then kills the four people from a suicidal website. Despite Lee seeing himself acting upon God’s will, his belief is being challenged.

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Mr McDreamy
programme.desc: A second generation rich man squanders his parents’ money and calls himself Mr McDreamy. When his parents finally have enough and cut him off financially, he establishes a “Mr McDreamy Training Academy” using various unconventional means to transform his four recruits into “Mr McDreamies” with hilarious results.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fiancé left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Princess & 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lam’s daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: My Love
programme.desc: Adapted from a Korean movie, this is the love story of school swimmer Zhou Xiao Qi and a transfer student You Yong Ci. Zhou falls in love with You at first sight in high school but You leaves suddenly one day without saying goodbye. As fate brings them back together years later, can they get the spark back in their relationship?

programme.title: Eternal Wave
programme.desc: Lin Xiang is a spy trying to rebuild an underground informant network in Shanghai after the Japanese Occupation. He meets a simple but righteous girl who acts as his wife in the secret mission. When Lin is captured after his identity was revealed, his “wife” comes to save him but can they escape from the foes?

programme.title: Monster Hunt
programme.desc: The pregnant queen of the monster realm flees a civil war and lands in human world, near Yung Ning Village. She seeks the help of a wimpy villager to become the surrogate father for her child, Wuba. From the time he was born, little Wuba embarks on a thrilling journey to escape from those who want to capture him at all costs.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: This silver screen epic, a prequel to Infernal Affairs, hit the astonishing $16.8 million box office mark one week after its premiere. The second installment of the Infernal Affairs trilogy brings audiences with ultimate suspense and high quality action scenes! Turning into a Chinese version of the popular Godfather series, Infernal Affairs II offers its viewers an even tighter plot with a brilliant cast led by Edison Chen, Shawn Yue, Carina Lau, Eric Tsang, Anthony Wong, and Francis Ng to supply top entertainment that has rarely been seen in modern Hong Kong cinema. A legend is born at the best of times. From the multiple award-winning team behind the mind-blowing blockbuster, the secrets are finally revealed in this most anticipating prequel: What drove police superintendent Wong (Anthony Wong) and crime boss Sam (Eric Tsang) against one another? How did two struggling moles Yan (Shawn Yue) and Ming (Edison Chen) begin their parallel fates? The keys lie in the hands of three: Sam's wife Mary (Carina Lau), ruthless kingpin Hau (Francis Ng), and righteous cop Luk (Hu Jun). The infernal gates are open to the worst of times...

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Legend of the Demon Cat
programme.desc: Adapted from a Japanese fantasy novel, a demon cat appears and breaks the peace of Chang'an city, causing a series of mysterious events. A poet and a Japanese monk band together to follow the trails left by the cat, leading them to discover a buried secret.

programme.title: Bell Chamber
programme.desc: Based on a Thai ghost story of Kuman Thong, the film revolves around a woman who has caused the death of her young brother a long time ago. When she returns to the old house where they lived before, she finds herself haunted by the spirit of her young brother wanting to take revenge for his death.

programme.title: Golden Job
programme.desc: A group of former mercenaries reunite to plan an epic heist: boosting a truckload of medicine held by a foreign intelligence agency to supply a refugee camp in need. When they find the truck is filled with stolen gold however, they realize they have been double-crossed by one of their own and putting the situation right will be an all-out war.

programme.title: Needing You
programme.desc: Office politics and love between co-workers complicates the lives of two computer-company employees in this romantic comedy starring Andy Lau and Sammi Cheng.

programme.title: Manhunt
programme.desc: In this movie directed by John Woo, lawyer Du goes on the run after he is framed for a murder. Veteran detective Yamura suspects the case to be more complicated than it seems, and while he understands Du better during the hunt, Yamura still doubts his innocence. Is the real killer lurking elsewhere? Is there a hidden conspiracy behind the murder?

programme.title: City Under Siege
programme.desc: When circus clown Sunny gets transformed into a super-powered mutant, he finds himself pitted against his fellow circus performers who were altered in the same accident, and who are now using their powers to wreak havoc around the city.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the “Gang of Five” in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: Fatal Visit
programme.desc: Yanny leaves Hong Kong for San Jose to visit her old friend Ling. Ling and her husband Tang seems to live an ideal and carefree life. However, during her five-day stay, Yanny uncovers the truth behind the façade as she reveals the unspeakable secrets that will propel all three down a fatal path of destruction.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yu’s beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: The Jade Raksha
programme.desc: A fearsome swordswoman known as The Jade Raksha appears in the martial arts world and begins killing people whose surname is Yan. A swordsman figures out who she is and asks her why. Apparently a Yan killed her family 18 years ago and she only has vengeance on her mind…

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: The Supreme Swordsman
programme.desc: After beating several famous swordsmen, Chin Wu-hsin (Pai Piao) of the Mo Shan clan challenges Supreme Swordsman (Wang Jung) to a duel, hoping to win his title, and is beaten and humiliated. The winner taunts him to find a Supreme Sword made by Old Eagle, a famous sword-maker (Ku Feng). When his offer to buy a sword from Old Eagle, is turned down, he challenges Old Eagle to a duel, and snatches his sword in a foul play. Old Eagle's own son Shih Yen-peh (Derek Yee) vows to avenge for his father...

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keeper’s daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: The Lady Professional
programme.desc: Lily Ho is perfectly cast as a gun-for-hire who always gets her man - in more ways than one! The cast and crew shot on location in Japanese scenic spots such as Mount Fuji; and there are plenty of over-the-top thrills, as Lily even masquerades as a nun.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: Journey of the Doomed
programme.desc: Journey Of The Doomed stars Tung Wei as a knight that finds himself protecting the life of a beautiful young lady, the lost Emperor's daughter and stalked by a bunch of assassins headed by kung fu actress extraordinaire Hui Ying-Hung.

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: Portrait In Crystal
programme.desc: Tragic deaths in the underworld cause leader "Yama" (Teng Wei-hao) to suspect a portrait in crystal with mysterious powers. He sends Hen Pan (Chen Hung) and Pai Pan (Hung Hsin-nan) to interrogate its creator, martial artist Lung Fei (Pai Piao)...

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: Constantly being abused by her cruel husband, the frail Chan Sau Ying awaits death from tuberculosis. The new servant girl Yi Wah, takes pity on her mistress’ plight and the pair proceed to drown him one evening. They dump his body in a nearby pond but Sau Ying believes that the man’s bloated corpse has risen from the bog to seek vengeance.

programme.title: Murderer Pursues
programme.desc: Wang Chung was a valued actor long before he became a director, but as a filmmaker, he helped create some of the most interesting thrillers Shaw Brothers ever released - including this fascinating crime saga of a Sino-Vietnamese crime gang. Danny Lee stars as a misunderstood refugee while Ray Lui plays a cop struggling against his own conscience to ensure that justice is upheld.

programme.title: Notorious Eight
programme.desc: The young Chen Chi-chin (Liu Yung) loses heavily to experienced gambler Hu Kuan-ten (Lo Lieh). His father loses at cards and dies of shock. Chen appeals to his uncle who summons seven fellow professional gamblers to carry out vengeance. Much more than a gambling film, this is a thrilling melting pot of martial arts stars, extortion, illicit love, poker-face vengeance, and all sorts of edge-of-your-seat gambling duels. Featuring two of the leading action stars of the era, Chen Kuen-tai and Lo Lieh, in a series of intense poker game standoffs. Famed director of the genre, Wong Jing, also has a guest appearance as one of the Notorious Eight.

programme.title: Let's Fall In Love
programme.desc: Da Yung, the son of a rich entrepreneur, meets Lian Lian, the niece of a kindergarten principal by chance. They get into a misunderstanding at the first meeting, causing Da Yung to lose his wallet. Further misunderstanding occurs when he tries to use her to act as his fiancé, in order to drive away two women whom he does not like…

programme.title: Ode to Gallantry
programme.desc: In this surprisingly light-hearted "Venoms" martial arts adventure, a lone wanderer is repeatedly mistaken for someone else and drawn into a number of violent battles.

programme.title: Beyond the Great Wall
programme.desc: Wang Zhao Jun refuses to bribe the imperial painter, so he draws an ugly portrait of her, preventing her from being selected by the Emperor until they meet in person. The painter ends up in exile and plots for Wang to marry the Hun’s warlord as a revenge. The Emperor rejects this, provoking a war which is only averted when Wang sacrifices herself.

programme.title: The Naval Commandos
programme.desc: The Chinese Navy is attempting to defend its coastline from a Japanese attack, they send their commando unit led by Cui Hsia into the mainland to enlist help to thwart the Japanese before they attack. The commandos enlist the help of Song San and Shiao Liu to kill the Japanese officers led by Shan Mao and destroy their attacking ships.

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: To the tune of the Osmonds hit song, this is a story of adolescent playfulness & innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together and teasingly meet two delightfully impish boys leading to the four to flirtatiously intermingle. However, the innocence of partner swapping eventually leads to a roller-coaster bouts of misunderstood emotions.

programme.title: The Silent Swordsman
programme.desc: This is adapted from Louis Cha’s “The Book and the Sword”. A young swordsman is tasked to lead a patriotic secret society to fight the traitorous general who colludes with the enemy. At the same time, he encounters a female warrior and two beautiful princesses, and is caught between all their affections for him.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70’s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sister’s magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: New Tales of the Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: A young musician Chi Chiang is hired by the manager of a popular band when the group's drummer/leader Charlie, quits to join a rival group. The new drummer becomes an immediate hit, causing Charlie to be very jealous. Furthermore, the young drummer's mother is dead set against him having a music career.

programme.title: Lion VS Lion
programme.desc: The traditional lion dance has never looked so good as in Lion VS Lion which captures the most impressive sequences of lion dancing on film. Besides being loaded with enjoyable martial arts chicanery, film historians can revel because it's also the first film that clearly demonstrates the intricacies and differences between the traditional Northern and Southern lion dancing techniques. The Five Venom alumnus and Chang Cheh discovery, Lo Meng, teams up with Liu Chia-liang protege Wang Yu, as they inadvertently turn from vagabond kung-fu school operators into anti-Ching, patriotic fighters.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Li Ching plays, Ah Chiao, a girl from a rural village stranded in the city, who befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are all poor, but Ah Chiao’s fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she ultimately learns money can't buy happiness.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: Pursuit of Vengeance
programme.desc: Kung Fu legend Ti Lung stars in the action movie as Fu Xue Hong, embarking on a epic journey of revenge for his father.

programme.title: The Flag of Iron
programme.desc: When super director Chang Cheh found new talent and blood with "The Five Venoms" actors, most of which were trained in the highly acrobatic Chinese opera and well versed with exotic martial arts weapons, this created a new spark for his use of bizarre weapons in his films. The Flag Of Iron is one of 20 movies that he directed featuring the utterly flabbergasting and physically exhausting action bits created by these five dudes. You have the good guys from the righteous clan versus the bad guys from the villainous clan and it's so filled with "don't-blink-or-you-will-miss-something" gags, you will need to watch it over and over again so you can see the things you missed.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insider’s look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiang’s popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: The Black Tavern
programme.desc: This sword-filled thriller centres on The Black Tavern – an inn where the down and dirty meet to plot nefarious doings. A bunch of villains are lured to the inn by a rumour about a valuable treasure being hidden there. After all the backstabbing and killings, they realise that it is a trap created to wipe them out once and for all…

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: In this hilarious sequel, Mr Big Potato opens an old-fashioned Chinese clinic, but his traditional methods are rejected by the sceptics of modern Hong Kong. Enter his buddy Mr Funny bone to rescue his business!

programme.title: Usurpers Of Emperor's Power
programme.desc: The last ruler of Tang, Li Yao (Chen Chia-chi) is deposed by Chao Kuang-jun (Wang Jung), the founder of the Sung Dynasty. Unfortunately his actions unleash a new plague - his brother Kuang-yi (Chao Kuo) - on the courts and his people. The marauding Kuang-yi rapes and plunders. As more people get involved, it turns into a bloody battlefield of betrayal. It is up to upright officials like Li Lang (Liu Yung) to put an end to it. But can one man take on the imperial army?

programme.title: Gossip Street
programme.desc: All neighbours gather to gossip in flat number 8 on the second floor of the Gossip Street apartment building! Most of the residents are common people from all walks of life and there is never a lack of laughter or sarcasm in the neighbourhood. However, when a local mobster wants to change the place into a gambling den, things get serious...

programme.title: Operation Lipstick
programme.desc: A professor’s assistant stole a micro-film storing the secret of a newly invented nuclear reactor and sells it to a crime syndicate. However, the micro-film accidentally falls into the hands of a nightclub dancer and a thief in the process, leading to them being relentlessly pursued by the crime syndicate to retrieve the micro-film.

programme.title: The Mirror and the Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully on their master’s birthday.

programme.title: Wild Wild East 1 Ep3

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep9

programme.title: Wild Wild East 1 Ep8
programme.desc: Wetlands - Wild Wild East’s wetland habitats are at risk. These marshes and bogs are the ancient home of the endangered Blanding’s Turtle. But each fall new turtles spring from the lake shores of Nova Scotia. If the vulnerable Blanding’s can make it through their first few years of life, they'll live for almost a century. But saving the turtle means protecting the wetlands, and all the other amphibians and reptiles that call the slow-moving waters home.

programme.title: Africa's Hunters 1 Ep1
programme.desc: The Hungry Leopard - A revolutionary thermal camera reveals the secret world of nocturnal predators. Follow along as one of the oldest-known leopards struggles to survive her fearsome neighbors: a pride of scavenging lions.

programme.desc: Roatan - Home to Earth’s second-largest barrier reef, Roatán is one of the world’s top dive spots–known for its rare black coral, low-lying nurse sharks, and fearsome-looking barracuda.

programme.title: Rooted 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Sweet Seduction - Discover the story of the much loved Sausage Tree, whose nectar filled blooms and sausage shaped fruits entice animals of all kinds, from insects to elephants. See how the very animals who rely on this generous tree ensure its proliferation.

programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 Ep1
programme.desc: Big Move - The Lilayi Elephant Nursery near Lusaka in Zambia is home to four orphan elephants. The two oldest, four-year- olds Musolole and Zambezi, have been here since they were just a few months old. These boisterous babies are out-growing the nursery and it’s time to move to big school. Two hundred miles away, in the heart of Kafue National Park, lies elephant heaven - Camp Phoenix, the project’s release facility, where older orphans are already adapting to life in the wild.

programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Zambia's Peaceful Primates - Kasanka National Park in Zambia is home to an unusual species of baboon. Kinda baboons have turned their backs on the aggressive displays of dominance usually associated with these large monkeys and lead altogether more peaceful lives. Living alongside one troop is a dedicated team of researchers whose mission it is to uncover these baboons’ secrets and understand what makes them who they are.
